<abstract><t>This paper presents a simple mechanism, based on &quot;threads&quot;, which can be used to prevent Multiprotocol Label Switching (MPLS) from setting up label switched path (LSPs) which have loops.  This memo defines an Experimental Protocol for the Internet community.</t></abstract>
